
To convert from 0-based indexing to 1-based indexing:
awk '{ if (NR > 1) { $1++; $2++; printf "%2d %2d\n", $1, $2 } else printf "%d\n", $1 }' snake13.txt

To convert from 1-based indexing to 0-based indexing:
awk '{ if (NR > 1) { $1--; $2--; printf "%2d %2d\n", $1, $2 } else printf "%d\n", $1 }' snake13.txt
